# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Claude Code CLI Config Template
#
# Claude Code CLI uses the Anthropic Messages API (/v1/messages).
# LiteLLM forwards to Huawei MaaS's Anthropic-compatible endpoint
# (/anthropic/v1/messages) via anthropic/ provider deployments in config.yaml.
#
# Model names are prefixed with claude- to avoid routing conflicts with
# OpenAI deployments that share the same base name. LiteLLM routes by
# model_name, so claude-glm-5.2 always hits the anthropic/ deployment
# (direct to Huawei MaaS Anthropic endpoint, no OpenAI conversion).
#
# Config is written to ~/.claude/settings.json (Claude Code's native settings
# file) using the env block. No shell exports or source needed — Claude Code
# reads this file automatically on startup.
#
# The actual settings.json content (JSON, not shell):
# {
#   "env": {
#     "ANTHROPIC_BASE_URL": "http://127.0.0.1:4000",
#     "ANTHROPIC_API_KEY": "sk-...",
#     "ANTHROPIC_MODEL": "claude-glm-5.2",
#     "ANTHROPIC_SMALL_FAST_MODEL": "claude-deepseek-v3.2"
#   }
# }
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
